headline: China’s GPRIMG Enters Long-Term LNG Supply Agreement with ConocoPhillips
summary: China’s Guangdong Pearl River Investment Management Group (GPRIMG) made headlines at the 29th World Gas Conference in Beijing with the announcement of its first long-term LNG purchase agreement, struck with U.S. energy major ConocoPhillips (NYSE:COP). The deal was signed on May 20 and disclosed through GPRIMG’s official WeChat account. It marks a significant step in the […]
